[I] Qt/C++ wrapper over minizip

[T] QuaZip is the C++ wrapper for Gilles Vollant's ZIP/UNZIP package (AKA
[T] Minizip) using Qt library.

[U] https://github.com/stachenov/quazip

[A] Sergei Tachenov
